data.eml:eml: Revision of the Genus Physiphora Fallén 1810 (Diptera: Ulidiidae: Ulidiinae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Elena P. Kameneva, Valery A. Kroneyev (2016): Revision of the Genus Physiphora Fallén 1810 (Diptera: Ulidiidae: Ulidiinae). Zootaxa 4087 (1): 1-88, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4087.1.1
